http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/Lok-Satta-thanks-Collector-SP/article14025965.ece

The Lok Satta udyama samstha Karimnagar district unit thanked Collector Neetu Prasad and Superintendent of Police D. Joel Davis for cancelling the weapon licence of tainted cop B. Mohan Reddy.In a press note here on Thursday, Lok Satta district president N. Srinivas and secretary Prakash Holla said that the Collector had instructed the tainted cop to surrender his weapon to the nearest police station. They reminded that the tainted cop had terrorised people with his service weapon while conducting the illegal money lending business in the district.